17c","tid":1952994,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:35:20.000Z","msg":"明明無說服力，就加啲術語聽落勁啲"},{"pid":"90b8f89125b1f85ccd3c441f43bcfa9cb40c1be2","tid":1952994,"uid":147721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:39:05.000Z","msg":"理論上彈的人中意講理論上係因為無做實驗 對實際上係點無信心"},{"pid":"1a48d62aa33d841d2bae7b1586d4cf3d5efe220d","tid":1952994,"uid":131245,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbac99db1ae9a4778de97e2945c85d9f5474a484","tid":1952994,"uid":138760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:32:18.000Z","msg":"好多時明明後面接住句野都無理論可言，點解咁鍾意講「理論上」?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:39:16.000Z","msg":"好多時物理實驗都係理論上，KEEP OTHER THINGS CONSTANT，實際上呢個世界無咁完滿，總有誤差，要睇你嘅tolerance。<br />\n<br />\n理論上個個連登仔都180，但實際上呢？"},{"pid":"9d54911fdac7513d3d19f48b8c7b43d1cba24928","tid":1952994,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理論上 啲人中意講理論上係因為無做實驗 對實際上係點無信心</blockquote>"},{"pid":"18cf04efc70dd632d42d4335e68dfdb51447db5c","tid":1952994,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:40:13.000Z","msg":"呢個係一個隱喻<br />\n<br />\n理論數據同實驗數據之間的差別<br />\n<br />\n引申到日常應用"},{"pid":"281c6ad481dc5bba2c152e4c3f83112ee8415825","tid":1952994,"uid":50429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:40:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得理論上係相對於實際上，實際上有一啲因素會影響一件事可唔可行，而從理論角度係未必會考慮嗰啲實際上嘅因素"},{"pid":"87814a9f766f602fb214bc247c73777975f3b2d7","tid":1952994,"uid":201197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:40:47.000Z","msg":"理論&lt;- 即係有假設<br />\n如果有人講『理論上』，即係佢有一啲假設，而唔肯定呢啲假設喺實際情況已出現或者會出現"},{"pid":"bdb5bca9e67f2ad6ce8e97e043e0989cd783e8c9","tid":1952994,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"理論上即係唔會發生"},{"pid":"a4b39d273601f919339be5ca00de9604cfbb18ad","tid":1952994,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:42:01.000Z","msg":"問蕭生佢最熟<br />\n<br />\n理論上預測<br />\n<br />\n事實上結果"},{"pid":"d685a8718118860b74b25ec7dd89cc224c77a414","tid":1952994,"uid":201197,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"你可唔可以買樓？<br />\n理論上可以，實際上唔可以<br />\n點解？<br />\n理論上，<strong>假設</strong>喺自由社會，有錢就可以買樓<br />\n實際上，我無錢"},{"pid":"f66a857ce8ef16061c9d7888c72f3c9099e2c0e2","tid":1952994,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"一大堆假設"},{"pid":"fad8d6f382e381372e54869d2051165cbf370b35","tid":1952994,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:06:07.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e5c48588dafec0af3a71b5558b5234c055b8b942","tid":1952994,"uid":20535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"照道理都唔一定有道理"},{"pid":"840961837df3072126546ed9a24aacf3d91b23c7","tid":1952994,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:09:22.000Z","msg":"哲學"},{"pid":"504e636754283e1dafa07a94ad4a8ce9ee72fab7","tid":1952994,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"upside of theory"},{"pid":"c50af76b24a39639fdfaa89f7ede298a4582310f","tid":1952994,"uid":333335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"如果個套理論係唔work 佢必然係有缺陷 理論唔完整<br />\n<br />\n所以「理論上可行 實質唔可行」<br />\n只係修飾維護理論嘅缺陷"},{"pid":"1cffe6a7f8bf137b9dc1a7eb75bf568f8df3329f","tid":1952994,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:17:01.000Z","msg":"Theoretically it shouldn&rsquo;t work, but it does"},{"pid":"222ce478843f9317c3c54d92a50c0c57ba7a5f35","tid":1952994,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"因為人既 愚蠢超乎想像<br />\n<br />\n例如usb type A 明明正面反面理論上插最多2次就得 偏偏大把人插第3次先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207b2e467d08cb37f4c780e96fccd858e1566db9","tid":1952994,"uid":273753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"其實即係 淨係諗既情況下"}]}